                    <h5 class="card-title">Web Design</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Focus on how you can help and benefit your user. Use simple words so that you don't confuse people</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mt-4 ">
            <div class="card border-0 p-3 p-md-2 px-lg-2">
                <img src="./images/service-2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Graphics Design Services">
                <div class="card-body p-0">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Graphics Design</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Focus on how you can help and benefit your user. Use simple words so that you don't confuse people</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mt-4 ">
            <div class="card border-0 p-3 p-md-2 ps-lg-2">
                <img src="./images/service-3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Content Creation Services">
                <div class="card-body p-0">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Content Creation</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Focus on how you can help and benefit your user. Use simple words so that you don't confuse people</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
